    "backbase_opportunities": "Sweden presents significant opportunities for Backbase across multiple vectors. The SME banking gap is the most immediate — no major Swedish bank has a truly modern SME digital banking platform. Wealth and private banking digitization is a strong fit given Sweden's savings culture and demand for hybrid advisory. Employee-facing tools (Assist) address the need to empower remaining branch and contact center staff as physical channels shrink. Core modernization programs at SEB, Handelsbanken, and Swedbank create natural entry points for Backbase as the engagement layer. Additionally, open banking and marketplace banking strategies require the kind of orchestration Backbase provides.",
